Paper: hep-th/0212229

Date: 2002-12-19

Title: Decomposing the SU(N) Connection and the Wu-Yang Potential

Authors: Yi-shi Duan and Peng-ming Zhang

Comments: 9 pages

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A17 (2002) 2283-2287

Based on the decomposition of SU(2) gauge field, we derive a generalizationof the decomposition theory for the SU(N) gauge field. We thus obtain theinvariant electro-magnetic tensors of SU(N) groups and the extended Wu-Yangpotentials. The sourceless solutions are also discussed.